{"tid":1299383,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【壽終正寢／撤回／暫緩】正視！檢討！穩住陣腳！","createTime":"2019-07-09T04:52:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T05:05:48.000Z","uid":94227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b42295251283493b42fb7f980645666a7339d99b","tid":1299383,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:52:27.000Z","msg":"林鄭用英文講到明: The bill is dead<br />\n國外一定會<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以為人民已取得勝利</span></strong></span><br />\n而林鄭亦stress左「壽 終 正 寢」<br />\n中間游離人仕<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">可能會收貨</span></strong></span> <br />\n事實上都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">已經出現唔同聲音</span></strong><br />\n為左<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">穩住我方陣腳 唔可以急</span></span></strong><br />\n大專學界必定要係我方有共識之後<br />\n再考慮與林鄭會面<br />\n否則只會比佢快刀斬亂麻<br />\n<br />\n個人認為抗爭走向至少有二<br />\n<br />\n一，繼續聚焦撤回同堅持其餘四大訴求<br />\n<br />\n二，淡化撤回訴求 改為聚焦警權問題<br />\n <br />\n但無論揀咩option <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣都好重要</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果揀（一）必定要向大眾（包括外國朋友）清楚解釋點解「壽終正寢」/ the bill is dead 唔應該收貨<br />\n更唔好比人覺得我地只係捉字蝨 而係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有法律依據</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n如果揀（二）就係正式既轉向 更加要做好文宣！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好急</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9c3de99e140daed5d2d2e5843444c3940fbee08f","tid":1299383,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d61e74759cf208bd5f903dd31c283b939272c1ef","tid":1299383,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"258504d8862bf8ad09321fa0c432046b2d6e1503","tid":1299383,"uid":94227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T04:54:40.000Z","msg":"Pu